title: Sawbones: The Four Humors
description:
This week on Sawbones, Dr. Sydnee and Justin wear a Taz T-shirt in a mall fashion show. Also, bile, blood and phlegm is discussed.

Music: "Medicines" by The Taxpayers (http://thetaxpayers.net)
author: sawbones@maximumfun.org (Justin McElroy)
